üí°‚ÄºÔ∏èMUST KNOW FACT ‚ÄºÔ∏èüí°

1. What‚Äôs SIM FREE and SIM LOCK iPhone?

‚úÖ SIM FREE iPhone is 100% Apple Store Set. 

‚ùå SIM LOCK iPhone is an iPhone locked to the original buyer who has signed the package under the Telco installment plan to ensure punctual payment of installment, and the phone is then being sold out by the original buyer to the market with an extremely lower price. (Even lower than the Official Apple US Price, the cheapest iPhone market in the world) 

2.How to differentiate SIM FREE (Apple Store Set) or SIM LOCK (Hybrid Unlock) iPhone?

-> FACTORY RESET. (Erase all content and settings)

-> UNBELIEVABLY LOW PRICE. (Comparing to Apple US)

: A SIM LOCK iPhone, which is secretly unlocked by outsiders through ‚ÄòTurbo Sim‚Äô or ‚ÄòHybrid Unlock‚Äô, cannot be factory reseted. Once reseted, the phone will be sim locked again. 

: A SIM FREE iPhone can do any Settings as advertised by Apple. You can reset a million times as you want. 

**With the latest technology, many Sim Lock iPhones ‚ÄòNo Need Turbo Sim‚Äô, sellers nowadays are using ‚ÄòHybrid Unlock‚Äô software to bypass the Sim Lock and advertise as ‚ÄòNo Sim Lock Phone‚Äô.
